dist/
*.app
*.dmg
*.pkg
*.xcarchive
*.zip
*.tar
*.tar.gz
*.tgz
*.7z

# Meeting media and downloaded model payloads are never source by default.
# A future small synthetic/licensed fixture requires explicit review and a
# narrow force-add with documented provenance.
